title: REGISTER_STREAMING_FILE_FROM_CACHE

0xCEAD2D4B// RegisterStreamingFileFromCache
void REGISTER_STREAMING_FILE_FROM_CACHE(char* resourceName, char* fileName, char* cacheString);Parameters:resourceName: The resource to add the asset to.fileName: A file name in the resource.cacheString: The string returned from REGISTER_RESOURCE_ASSET on the server.Experimental: This native may be altered or removed in future versions of CitizenFX without warning.Registers a dynamic streaming asset from the server with the GTA streaming module system.
